meta.name: Stable Artist Hunter
meta.author: Omnitool.ai team
meta.description: Find the artist from those who are trained data in the Stable Diffusion model

data.instruction:
Based on the following description of a desired style or theme, I would like you to recommend an artist who best represents this style or theme. Please recommend only from the list provided and respond with the artist's name only, no other details are necessary.
